            "content_html": "<h2 id=\"测试说明\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#测试说明\">#</a> 测试说明</h2>\n<p>这是一篇测试文章，用于验证以下功能：</p>\n<ul>\n<li>文章在「Java代码审计」专栏下正常展示</li>\n<li>文章同时出现在博客首页</li>\n<li><code>_posts/Java代码审计/</code> 子目录结构正常工作</li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"代码审计测试\"><a class=\"anchor\" href=\"#代码审计测试\">#</a> 代码审计测试</h2>\n<pre class=\"shiki shiki-themes vitesse-light vitesse-dark\" style=\"background-color:#ffffff;--shiki-dark-bg:#121212;color:#393a34;--shiki-dark:#dbd7caee\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-java\"><span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">// 测试代码块是否正常渲染</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">public</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> class</span><span style=\"color:#2E8F82;--shiki-dark:#5DA994\"> Test</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> </span><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">    public</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> static</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> void</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\"> main</span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">(</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\">String</span><span style=\"color:#a65e2b;--shiki-dark:#d4976c\">[</span><span style=\"color:#a65e2b;--shiki-dark:#d4976c\">]</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> args</span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> </span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">{</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\">        String</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\"> input</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\"> =</span><span style=\"color:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\"> \"</span><span style=\"color:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">test&#x3C;script>alert(1)&#x3C;/script></span><span style=\"color:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#A0ADA0;--shiki-dark:#758575DD\">        // 这是一个典型的 XSS 示例</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">        System</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"color:#B07D48;--shiki-dark:#BD976A\">out</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">.</span><span style=\"color:#59873A;--shiki-dark:#80A665\">println</span><span style=\"color:#a65e2b;--shiki-dark:#d4976c\">(</span><span style=\"color:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#B56959;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D\">输入: </span><span style=\"color:#B5695977;--shiki-dark:#C98A7D77\">\"</span><span style=\"color:#AB5959;--shiki-dark:#CB7676\"> +</span><span style=\"color:#393A34;--shiki-dark:#DBD7CAEE\"> input</span><span style=\"color:#a65e2b;--shiki-dark:#d4976c\">)</span><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">;</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#999999;--shiki-dark:#666666\">    </span><span style=\"color:#1e754f;--shiki-dark:#4d9375\">}</span></span>\n<span class=\"line\"><span style=\"color:#2993a3;--shiki-dark:#5eaab5\">}</span></span></code></pre>\n<hr />\n<blockquote>\n<p>如果这篇测试文章在首页和「Java代码审计」专栏中都能正常显示，说明目录结构和配置都正确。</p>\n</blockquote>\n",
